summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting from the State of Washington, Department of natural Resources, two easements for storm drain outfalls over portions of the following State-owned lands: The bed of East Waterway in front of Blocks 376, 386 and vacated 6th Avenue Southwest, Seattle Tide Lands, Plate 24, and the harbor area in front of portions of Blocks 477 and 478, Seattle Tide Lands, Extension No. 1, Plate 70, all in King County, Washington.
